# Wombat Home Loans

> Sydney mortgage broker specialising in complex finance for expats, international professionals and first-home buyers.

## About

Wombat Home Loans is run by Tom Carr, a Sydney-based mortgage broker with 20+ years of institutional banking experience (Citigroup, UBS, RBS, Commonwealth Bank). Tom helps clients navigate the Australian property market — particularly expats and international professionals buying their first Australian home.

Wombat Home Loans is a credit representative of Finsure Finance & Insurance Pty Ltd (Australian Credit Licence 384704).

- Location: Beecroft, Sydney, NSW, Australia
- Access to 40+ lenders
- No cost to borrowers (commission-paid by lenders)

## Services

- Home loan broking (owner-occupied and investment)
- Refinancing
- Expat and non-resident lending
- First-home buyer guidance
- Construction and renovation loans
- Borrowing capacity assessments

